{"ID":270373, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"373\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs372.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs374.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 373<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">Gods; and then we shall see as we are seen,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> and be as our God<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and He as His Father.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> I want to\n  reason a little on this subject. I learned it by translating the papyrus which is now in my house.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Abraham&rsquo;s Reasoning<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I learned a testimony concerning Abraham, and he reasoned concerning the God of heaven.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> &ldquo;In\n  order to do that,&rdquo; said he, &ldquo;suppose we have two facts:<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> that supposes another fact may exist&mdash;two\n  men on the earth, one wiser than the other, would logically show that another who is wiser than the\n  wisest may exist. Intelligences exist one above another,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> so that there is no end to them.&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If Abraham reasoned thus&mdash;If Jesus Christ was the Son of God, and John discovered that God\n  the Father of Jesus Christ<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> had a Father,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> you may suppose that He had a Father also. Where was\n  there ever a son without a father? And where was there ever a father without first being a son?\n  Whenever did a tree or anything spring into existence without a progenitor? And everything comes\n  in this way. Paul says that which is earthly is in the likeness of that which is heavenly,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> Hence if\n  Jesus had a Father,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> can we not believe that He had a Father also? I despise the idea of being scared\n  to death at such a doctrine, for the Bible is full of it.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I want you to pay particular attention to what I am saying. Jesus said that the Father wrought\n  precisely in the same way as His Father had done before Him.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> As the Father had done before? He\n  laid down His life, and took it up<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> the same as His Father had done before. He did as He was sent,\n  to lay down His life and take it up again; and then was committed unto Him the keys.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> I know it is\n  good reasoning.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Church Being Purged<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I have reason to think that the Church is being purged.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> I saw Satan fall from heaven,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> and the\n  way they ran was a caution. All these are wonders<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> and marvels in our eyes<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> in these last days. So\n  long as men are under the law of God,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> they have no fears&mdash;they do not scare themselves.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I want to stick to my text, to show that when men open their lips against these truths<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> they do\n  not injure me, but injure themselves. To the law and to the testimony,<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> for these prin-<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109552\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109552)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109552)\">1 Cor. 13:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110592\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110592)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110592)\">1 Jn. 3:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110674\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110674)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110674)\">Rev. 1:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106047\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106047)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106047)\">Gen. 24:3,7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106554\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106554)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106554)\">Neh. 1:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107508\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107508)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107508)\">Dan. 2:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110772\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110772)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110772)\">Rev. 11:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112874\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112874)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112874)\">Ether 8:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116827\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116827)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116827)\">Moses 6:43<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117037\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117037)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117037)\">Abr. 3:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117020\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117020)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117020)\">Abr. 3:8,16-17,19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109394\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109394)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109394)\">Rom. 15:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110675\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110675)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110675)\">Rev. 1:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109612\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109612)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109612)\">1 Cor. 15:46-48<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110227\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110227)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110227)\">Heb. 8:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116149\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116149)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116149)\">D&amp;C 128:13-14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109759\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109759)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109759)\">Eph. 1:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108672\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108672)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108672)\">John 5:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108753\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108753)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108753)\">John 10:17-18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108289\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108289)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108289)\">Matt. 28:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116204\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116204)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116204)\">D&amp;C 128:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108500\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108500)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108500)\">Luke 10:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106861\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106861)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106861)\">Ps. 119:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106856\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106856)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106856)\">Ps. 118:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108144\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108144)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108144)\">Matt. 21:42<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112545\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112545)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112545)\">3 Ne. 5:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112824\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112824)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112824)\">Morm. 9:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107216\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107216)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107216)\">Isa. 51:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109257\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109257)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109257)\">Rom. 3:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107041\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107041)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107041)\">Isa. 8:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}